HEADWORD: Broking
<hw>Bro"king</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
a broker or brokers, or to brokerage.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Redeem from <qex>broking</qex> pawn the blemished crown.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

